    span Hello #{fullName || 'there'}
block content
    h4.
        Student Account created
    p.
        A new #{organization} student account has been created for you.
        To proceed with the login. Kindly click on the following link.
    p.
        You will use the following username to access your account.
    div.centered
        h2 #{username}
    a(href=link)
        span Create a password
